														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2485443">
									

<p>Mmm. I figured it out way too early, I guess (the title in conjunction with the first paragraph was enough for me to guess, the initials were enough for me to be sure), so as a result most of my thoughts were just &quot;I wonder when it's going to use 'it's a me'.&quot;</p>
<p>Of course, outside of the buildup to that line, there's not much else to this, and there isn't much here for me to&#8230; really feel anything about this. I guess the line is meant to be funny, but then the reveal doesn't make rereading rewarding at all, because there aren't many references to the games and the characters don't seem to act much like they normally do (for as thin characters they are in the original works).</p>

